    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shoemakers' knives used to even the heel of a clog on the inside. It consists of a long, double-edged blade curved upwards at the end and a straight wooden handle.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
